I'm ok with nerfing Rylai's, definitely deserved, it's just the fact that this adds up to the whole other nerfed ap items + Blue buff not giving 15% ap anymore.

I think next patch we'll be seeing rarely something different than  {{champion:84}} or {{champion:7}}, or ad assassins.

Many builds will shift into either {{item:3027}}  or {{item:3030}}

Actually, damage Mages like {{champion:101}} {{champion:99}} {{champion:103}} will build {{item:3285}} again.

Otherwise champions like {{champion:50}} {{champion:30}} and the nonexistent {{champion:163}} will probably still be building {{item:3116}} 

They won't feel the nerf as much because they don't depend upon their burst, but their sustained damage, which is easier to output with a  consistent slow.
